Address	Register	Access	Description
0x0000	CTRL	RW	Start transfer
0x0004	STATUS	RO	BUSY/DONE/ERROR
0x0008	SRC_ADDR	RW	Source address
0x000C	DST_ADDR	RW	Destination address
0x0010	LENGTH	RW	Transfer length
0x0014	IRQ_STATUS	RO	Interrupt status
0x0018	IRQ_CLEAR	WO	Clear interrupt

Register Definitions :

CTRL Register (0x0000)
Bit	Name	Description
[0]	START	Start DPU transfer

STATUS Register (0x0004)
Bit	Name	Description
[0]	BUSY	Transfer active
[1]	DONE	Transfer complete
[2]	ERROR	Error detected

SRC_ADDR Register (0x0008)
Bits	Description
[7:0]	Source SRAM address

DST_ADDR Register (0x000C)
Bits	Description
[7:0]	Destination SRAM address

LENGTH Register (0x0010)
Bits	Description
[15:0]	Number of words to transfer

IRQ_STATUS Register (0x0014)
Bit	Description
[0]	Interrupt pending

IRQ_CLEAR Register (0x0018)
Bit	Description
[0]	Clear interrupt
